<p>If you&amp;rsquo;ve looked around and decided on self-publishing your book with a print-on-demand, a subsidy, co-publishing company, or other format, there are certain steps that need to be taken before you think about signing a contract, or creating an e-book. And, it&amp;rsquo;s important you realize that this road to publication will cost money that you may not recoup. You will need to work diligently to ensure a return on your investment.</p>

